<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Hexatopia - 피드</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #4caf50;">Hexatopia 헥사토피아</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">홈</a>
            <a href="/feed">피드</a>
            <a href="/breeding">사육실</a>
            <a href="/map">곤충지도</a>
            <a href="/market">마켓</a>
            <a href="/forum">포럼</a>
            <a href="/admin" style="color: #ff9800;">관제탑</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>실시간 피드 및 갤러리 <span style="font-size:14px; color:var(--text-muted);">[인스타그램 / 핀터레스트 카드 레이아웃]</span></h2>
<div class="grid">
    <% feeds.forEach(feed => { %>
        <div class="card">
            <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:10px;">
                <span class="badge success"><%= feed.type %></span>
                <strong><%= feed.author %></strong>
            </div>
            <div style="background:#333; width:100%; height:180px; border-radius:6px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#666; margin-bottom:15px;">
                [ 곤충/필드 스냅 이미지 영역 ]
            </div>
            <h3><%= feed.title %></h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted);"><%= feed.content %></p>
            <div style="color:var(--accent-color);">♥ 좋아요 <%= feed.likes %>개</div>
        </div>
    <% }) %>
</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
